    '{"id":"01KE82GQYHNR8SCQPEYYKE4GNK","title":"EASE // MiD - Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Podcast Production and Guest Scheduling**\n\nThe team is focused on filling guest slots and progressing podcast content amid scheduling challenges.\n\n- **The latest podcast episode went live yesterday along with its blog post**, confirming on-schedule content delivery (07:10)  \n    - Paula shared that the blog and episode are aligned for launch, maintaining the planned content calendar  \n    - Josh emphasized the urgent need to secure new guests, as he currently has no scheduled episodes  \n    - Paula has prepared and expanded a contact list with **5–6 new prospects**, targeting manufacturing and speaking event participants to improve bookings  \n    - Josh agreed to review the updated list and begin outreach, aiming to boost guest acquisition soon\n\n- **Due to guest booking delays, the team will create a podcast episode recap blog** as a fallback for the next release (11:20)  \n    - Josh suggested focusing on a recap of last year’s best episodes as a timely content piece  \n    - Paula committed to drafting the recap and sharing it with Josh and Sydney for feedback, ensuring continuity despite guest scheduling gaps  \n    - This approach mitigates risk of missing content deadlines and keeps audience engagement steady  \n    - The recap will also set expectations for 2026’s podcast roadmap, reinforcing forward-looking messaging\n\n## **Video Production and Audio Refinement**\n\nThe video team is finalizing audio approvals and starting animation work to meet delivery targets.\n\n- **Audio for the OTG video has been approved, allowing animation work to start with a first cut expected next week** (09:16)  \n    - Paula noted that the team is addressing Josh’s feedback on audio mixing to improve quality  \n    - The animation timeline depends on completing audio, with some team members on holiday this week, slightly impacting speed  \n    - Josh expressed eagerness to finish videos soon, highlighting a few remaining audio concerns he couldn’t overlook  \n    - The plan includes rolling out animation for additional videos after the OTG piece, aiming for a smooth production flow\n\n- **Ongoing collaboration between Josh and the creative team is critical to finalize videos on schedule** (09:50)  \n    - Paula asked for any further video input; Josh confirmed no additional comments but stressed finalization urgency  \n    - The phased approach helps manage workload and maintain quality through iterative reviews  \n    - Timely completion of these videos supports broader marketing and content strategies planned for early 2026\n\n## **Outreach Campaign and Contact Management**\n\nThe outreach campaign is preparing to activate with a refreshed and targeted contact list to improve guest outreach effectiveness.\n\n- **A refined contact list with recent additions targets industry-specific guests for upcoming podcasts** (07:55)  \n    - Paula filtered contacts to include those linked to manufacturing and public speaking opportunities, increasing relevance  \n    - Josh had already reviewed part of the list and requested additional contacts to widen reach  \n    - Sharing and approval of this list enables the outreach campaign to start promptly, improving pipeline velocity  \n    - The campaign''s success metrics will likely hinge on contact responsiveness and conversion rates into guest bookings\n\n- **This outreach effort is essential to counteract current guest booking challenges and sustain content flow** (08:45)  \n    - The campaign complements ongoing content production by filling the pipeline with qualified prospects  \n    - Paula’s proactive list updates reflect an adaptive strategy responding to market and scheduling realities  \n    - The outreach aligns with broader goals to increase podcast guest diversity and industry relevance\n\n## **Process Adjustments and Content Strategy**\n\nFlexibility in content formats and workflows is being applied to maintain momentum despite resource constraints.\n\n- **Introducing a review section for the podcast is under consideration to add fresh content without guest dependency** (10:40)  \n    - Josh plans to record the review voiceover himself, reducing reliance on external guests  \n    - This format change adds variety and keeps the podcast engaging during guest scarcity  \n    - Paula’s team is ready to support production once recordings are available, maintaining production cadence  \n    - This adjustment reflects a pragmatic approach to content creation balancing quality and feasibility\n\n- **The team agreed to maintain close communication via Slack to ensure smooth progress during Bailey’s absence** (12:15)  \n    - Paula will be the main point of contact and is available for immediate support  \n    - This setup ensures operational continuity and quick responses to any issues  \n    - It also supports collaborative review cycles for content and production deliverables\n\n## **Timeline and Resource Coordination**\n\nClear deadlines and resource availability shape the project’s immediate next steps and risk management.\n\n- **Animation first cut delivery is targeted for next week, contingent on final audio adjustments and partial team availability** (09:20)  \n    - Holiday schedules are slowing production slightly but are factored into delivery plans  \n    - Paula’s team is managing workload to avoid delays and maintain quality standards  \n    - Josh’s prompt feedback remains crucial to keep timelines intact  \n    - Meeting these deadlines supports early 2026 marketing campaigns and content launches\n\n- **Guest acquisition efforts need acceleration to avoid content gaps beyond the next episode** (07:35)  \n    - Without new guests lined up, fallback content like recaps become necessary to sustain publishing cadence  \n    - The outreach campaign and contact list expansion are critical to mitigate this risk  \n    - Clear ownership of contact review and follow-up is assigned to Josh with Paula’s support  \n    - This coordination ensures that future podcast episodes remain on track and aligned with strategic goals","outline":null,"keywords":["Podcast episodes","Guest outreach","Contact list","Video production","Audio mixing","Content recap"],"overview":"- **Podcast Episode Launch:** Latest episode and blog post launched on schedule, aligning with content calendar.  \n- **Guest Acquisition Urgency:** Josh lacks scheduled episodes, emphasizing need for prompt outreach to new prospects.  \n- **Recap Blog Strategy:** Team will create a recap of last year’s episodes to maintain audience engagement amid guest delays.  \n- **Animation Production Timeline:** Audio for OTG video approved; animation starts next week with a focus on quality.  \n- **Refined Outreach List:** New contact list targets industry-specific guests, accelerating outreach for podcast bookings.  \n- **Flexible Content Approach:** Consideration of podcast review sections to mitigate guest dependency and keep content engaging.","action_items":"\n**Paula Ocampo**\nShare the updated guest contact list with Josh for review and campaign initiation (07:42)\nHighlight recently added contacts and explain justification for each to Josh (09:14)\nContinue working on audio animation for OTG video and provide the first cut next week for Josh’s review (09:45)\nStart drafting the podcast recap content covering last year’s highlights and plans for 2026, and share drafts with Josh and Sydney (11:59)\nBe available on Slack to support Josh during Bailey’s absence (12:08)\n\n**Josh Santo**\nReview and verify the updated guest contact list shared by Paula to select podcast invitees (08:18)\nRecord the voiceover for the podcast review section if proceeding with that addition (10:36)\nPrioritize securing and scheduling podcast guests to maintain episode pipeline (10:26)\n"},"duration":12.609999656677246,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Josh Santo"},{"id":1,"name":"Paula Ocampo"}],"sentences":[{"text":"This meeting is being recorded.","index":0,"end_time":5.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Hey, Josh.","index":1,"end_time":342.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":341.89,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Hi, Paula.","index":2,"end_time":344.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.25,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":3,"end_time":345.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Great.","index":4,"end_time":345.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":345.53,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":5,"end_time":346.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":345.85,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I''m doing all right.","index":6,"end_time":348.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":347.09,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"How was your holidays?","index":7,"end_time":350.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.17,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Too short, but good.","index":8,"end_time":352.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":350.85,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Same, Same.","index":9,"end_time":354.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":352.93,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":10,"end_time":355.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":355.33,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I needed two more weeks.","index":11,"end_time":357.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":355.97,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":12,"end_time":358.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":357.65,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":13,"end_time":359.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":358.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s how it goes.","index":14,"end_time":360.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.86,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":362.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.1,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Did you travel?","index":16,"end_time":364.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Go anywhere?","index":17,"end_time":365.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"No, I stayed with my family here, my city.","index":18,"end_time":369.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.78,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"But I had a really great time.","index":19,"end_time":370.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.3,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":20,"end_time":371.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":370.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So, yeah, I needed two more weeks just to chill and stay with them.","index":21,"end_time":376.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":371.54,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":22,"end_time":376.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And where are you located?","index":23,"end_time":378.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":377.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I''m based in Bogota, Colombia.","index":24,"end_time":381.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":379.22,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Oh, Colombia.","index":25,"end_time":382.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Cool.","index":26,"end_time":383.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":382.86,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yes.","index":27,"end_time":384.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.19,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":28,"end_time":386.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":385.47,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So for today, let me share my screen.","index":29,"end_time":389.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":386.51,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We can get started.","index":30,"end_time":390.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":389.71,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So Bailey is going to be out this week and next week, so.","index":31,"end_time":406.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.27,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, just.","index":32,"end_time":409.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":408.59,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Just for you to know.","index":33,"end_time":410.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":409.39,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Can you see my screen now?","index":34,"end_time":412.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":411.18,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I can, yeah.","index":35,"end_time":413.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":412.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Great.","index":36,"end_time":414.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":414.06,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So for today, I have some podcast updates.","index":37,"end_time":419.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":415.74,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We''ll go through content updates as well, and the outreach outreach campaign and the video plan.","index":38,"end_time":426.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.66,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we''re starting with the podcast updates.","index":39,"end_time":430.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.06,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"The episode we were Jeep is now live.","index":40,"end_time":433.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":430.86,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"It went live yesterday, so same as the blog.","index":41,"end_time":438.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":433.9,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I share it with Sydney last.","index":42,"end_time":439.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":438.39,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Last week or last two weeks?","index":43,"end_time":441.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.15,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I don''t remember exactly, but I think it''s a schedule to go live next week, so we''re all good there.","index":44,"end_time":447.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":441.51,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And I wanted to ask you, do you have any upcoming episodes scheduled?","index":45,"end_time":455.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.11,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I don''t have.","index":46,"end_time":456.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":455.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I don''t have anybody.","index":47,"end_time":457.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.87,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s why I need to get the contact stuff going.","index":48,"end_time":461.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.07,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":49,"end_time":462.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.48,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I have the contact list ready for you, so I''m gonna share after this goal so you can take a quick look.","index":50,"end_time":468.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.84,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I added some new contacts, just like five or six more to see if you''re okay with that.","index":51,"end_time":475.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":469.04,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We can review it right here if you want.","index":52,"end_time":478.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":476.08,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":53,"end_time":479.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.56,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Just.","index":54,"end_time":479.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":479.52,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So, yeah, the ones highlighted in yellow are the ones that I added recently from Michelangelo.","index":55,"end_time":491.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":484.4,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Right here.","index":56,"end_time":491.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":491.19,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I can share this with you and if you''re okay, we can start running the campaign.","index":57,"end_time":498.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":493.75,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I think I already looked at these.","index":58,"end_time":501.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":498.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, I think.","index":59,"end_time":504.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":503.83,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I think you said this right here.","index":60,"end_time":506.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":504.59,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Ah, okay.","index":61,"end_time":507.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":507.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then I asked for more.","index":62,"end_time":509.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":508.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":63,"end_time":510.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.07,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I think this is pretty good.","index":64,"end_time":518.329,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":513.11,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":65,"end_time":527.009,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.569,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":66,"end_time":527.449,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":527.009,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yes, send me the list.","index":67,"end_time":528.809,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":527.449,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I''ll have to check on a couple things.","index":68,"end_time":530.569,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":528.809,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":69,"end_time":531.809,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.289,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Let me highlight the ones that I added recently.","index":70,"end_time":534.009,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.809,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":71,"end_time":538.169,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.769,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Try to find people in manufacturing, but also that have speaking, podcast or events.","index":72,"end_time":544.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":538.169,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So you can take a look here in the reasoning why.","index":73,"end_time":548.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":544.71,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And I mean, I can add more if you want.","index":74,"end_time":552.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.99,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Whatever you prefer.","index":75,"end_time":553.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.63,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Got it.","index":76,"end_time":555.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.95,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":77,"end_time":556.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":556.31,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":78,"end_time":557.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":556.79,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And.","index":79,"end_time":559.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":559.03,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Then for the video plan, and thanks so much for sharing all the feedback for the mix audio.","index":80,"end_time":569.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":564.07,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Our team is.","index":81,"end_time":570.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":569.59,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Is working on those and we''re already working on the animation for the otg since the audio was approved.","index":82,"end_time":577.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":570.19,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So it will take a couple of days.","index":83,"end_time":580.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":578.87,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"But I''ll share the first cut probably next week for your review.","index":84,"end_time":584.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.79,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":85,"end_time":585.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":585.349,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know if you have any comments or anything else to add for the videos.","index":86,"end_time":591.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":587.19,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"No, just eager to finish them up.","index":87,"end_time":594.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":591.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think we''re real close on the audio.","index":88,"end_time":596.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"There''s just some moments where, you know, I just.","index":89,"end_time":599.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.11,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I just couldn''t let some.","index":90,"end_time":601.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.73,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Some things go.","index":91,"end_time":603.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.05,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":92,"end_time":604.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.65,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So, yeah, our team is.","index":93,"end_time":605.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":604.73,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Is being on holidays this week, part of this week, but we''ll have that ready really soon so we can get started on the animation for the rest of the videos.","index":94,"end_time":615.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.97,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And yeah, last we have our client portal, so.","index":95,"end_time":621.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":617.33,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know if you have anything in your agenda for today.","index":96,"end_time":624.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.49,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Anything else?","index":97,"end_time":625.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":624.37,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"No, I just really need to get some guests lined up and then get those videos done.","index":98,"end_time":635.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":626.22,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":99,"end_time":637.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.86,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I know you mentioned during our last call to include like a review section to the podcast.","index":100,"end_time":644.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":637.74,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I don''t know if this is something you want to.","index":101,"end_time":646.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":644.74,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Still doing.","index":102,"end_time":648.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":647.26,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we can start working on it or.","index":103,"end_time":650.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":648.3,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''ll just have to record that.","index":104,"end_time":655.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":651.19,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So record the voiceover.","index":105,"end_time":658.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.07,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Reviews.","index":106,"end_time":664.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":663.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":107,"end_time":665.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":664.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":108,"end_time":666.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.51,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And then so we probably.","index":109,"end_time":668.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":666.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I probably won''t have anything recorded by the time we want to do.","index":110,"end_time":671.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":668.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"We typically do the next episode.","index":111,"end_time":673.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":672.15,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Last time we were in this situation, we ended up just focusing on the blog post side of things and like creating a.","index":112,"end_time":683.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like a recap blog.","index":113,"end_time":685.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":683.61,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I''m wondering if we can do that this time since I just.","index":114,"end_time":691.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":686.41,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I really don''t see me finding a guest and recording with them by next week.","index":115,"end_time":697.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":691.97,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":116,"end_time":698.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Probably we can do a recap of last year''s best vlogs or something like that.","index":117,"end_time":703.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":698.49,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, with the team.","index":118,"end_time":705.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.37,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"That''s a good idea.","index":119,"end_time":707.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.09,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Kicking off the new year.","index":120,"end_time":708.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":707.13,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You know, here''s what we did.","index":121,"end_time":710.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.13,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Here''s what.","index":122,"end_time":712.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":711.61,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Here''s who we talked to.","index":123,"end_time":713.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":712.21,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Here''s what we learned.","index":124,"end_time":714.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.21,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Here''s what we''re hoping to do in 2026, something like that.","index":125,"end_time":719.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":714.89,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, sounds good.","index":126,"end_time":720.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":719.53,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I''ll get working on.","index":127,"end_time":722.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":720.65,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I''ll get started on.","index":128,"end_time":724.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":722.97,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"On that and I''ll share some drafts with you and Sydney.","index":129,"end_time":727.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":724.17,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":130,"end_time":728.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.17,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So you can take a look.","index":131,"end_time":729.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":728.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":132,"end_time":730.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":729.91,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"4:13pm thank you.","index":133,"end_time":733.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.35,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I think that''s.","index":134,"end_time":734.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.43,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"That''s all I have for today.","index":135,"end_time":735.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":734.31,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I''ll be on Slack available.","index":136,"end_time":737.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":736.15,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I think Bailey is not available on Slack.","index":137,"end_time":741.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":737.83,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"But just let me know if you need anything.","index":138,"end_time":743.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":741.63,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":139,"end_time":744.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.67,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"We''ll do.","index":140,"end_time":744.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.31,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":141,"end_time":745.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":745.27,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":142,"end_time":746.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":745.99,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Thank you, Josh.","index":143,"end_time":747.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":746.63,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay, thanks, pa. Bye.","index":144,"end_time":749.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"}],"dateString":"2026-01-07T21:05:00.000Z","host_email":"paula.ocampo@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us04we