speaker_id":2,"start_time":490.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t think we''re changing any.","index":170,"end_time":493.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":491.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I do want to talk about specifically that Reddit thread that the pieces that I sent you to kind of understand it, because I don''t know that I understand it, but I don''t think we''re at a point right now where people are going in and saying, Chad, GPT, what''s a good replacement for RingCentral?","index":171,"end_time":505.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":493.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just don''t think we''re there yet.","index":172,"end_time":506.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":505.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t think people are there.","index":173,"end_time":507.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":506.59,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t think that''s really something that happens today.","index":174,"end_time":510.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":508.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s definitely not where the majority of.","index":175,"end_time":512.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":510.71,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"People are doing correct.","index":176,"end_time":512.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":512.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think they''re still going into Google or Bing or whatever the freak it is and asking those questions for replacement.","index":177,"end_time":518.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":512.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I don''t think that changes.","index":178,"end_time":520.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":518.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But my thought is, how do you.","index":179,"end_time":524.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":521.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"This brings up a valid point.","index":180,"end_time":525.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":524.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think that