nk are great to build and it also rates us.","index":233,"end_time":682.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":673.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''ll also help for SEO.","index":234,"end_time":683.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":682.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"These Pages explicitly tell AI TechMode belongs in the same conversations as these providers.","index":235,"end_time":691.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I mean, I got a whole thing here of stuff we''re gonna review and work through.","index":236,"end_time":698.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":693.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But this kind of goes back to, I''ll stop sharing.","index":237,"end_time":703.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":700.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, you know, I kind of backed off for, you know, Colin, you were all about, let''s go after the ring, let''s really call him out by name.","index":238,"end_time":710.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I''m like, I don''t know if I want to do that.","index":239,"end_time":711.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":710.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"AI is basically telling me you gotta attack them.","index":240,"end_time":715.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":712.51,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, you gotta go at them and say why you''re the same or why you''re different or say why you''re the same and different.","index":241,"end_time":720.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":715.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":242,"end_time":721.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":720.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":243,"end_time":721.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":721.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So anyways, that''s kind of what I got at all that.","index":244,"end_time":724.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":722.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text"