384,"end_time":1185.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1184.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right.","index":385,"end_time":1185.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1185.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I understand.","index":386,"end_time":1185.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1185.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"2026 strategy.","index":387,"end_time":1192.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1190.9,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Stop writing generic blog posts.","index":388,"end_time":1193.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1192.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Understood.","index":389,"end_time":1194.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1193.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Stop chasing traffic.","index":390,"end_time":1195.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1194.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Start optimizing for AI trust factors.","index":391,"end_time":1197.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1195.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think this is actually what got me a little bit.","index":392,"end_time":1199.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1197.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I''m like, shit, we should start doing that.","index":393,"end_time":1201.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":394,"end_time":1201.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1201.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s a great goal for us in 2026, especially if it''s going to enhance our SEO anyways.","index":395,"end_time":1207.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1201.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I agree with all that.","index":396,"end_time":1210.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1208.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And unless you guys had anything else you wanted to add there.","index":397,"end_time":1212.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1210.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, just a few ideas there that I was thinking was, I don''t think it''s like, stop writing blogs.","index":398,"end_time":1216.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1212.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it''s changing the positioning of blogs to.","index":399,"end_time":1220.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1216.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can talk about comparisons.","index":400,"end_time":1222.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can talk about.","index":401,"end_time":1223.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You guys actually just linked to it from one of the pages.","index":402,"end_time":1226.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1223.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The MSP or the virtual ip.","index":403,"end_time":1227.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1226.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t remember specifically, but it was like.","index":404,"end_time":1229.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it was the MSP.","index":405,"end_time":1230.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was like how MSPs buy phone systems was like, that was a great article.","index":406,"end_time":1234.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Great thing to point something to.","index":407,"end_time":1236.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Definitely something that someone wants to read through as they''re trying to go through that difficult decision process.","index":408,"end_time":1240.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So those are the types of articles I think that would be more beneficial moving forward.","index":409,"end_time":1244.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I agree.","index":410,"end_time":1246.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1245.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I agree with you.","index":411,"end_time":1247.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1246.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I actually have started doing A little bit of that with.","index":412,"end_time":1250.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1247.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s why I kind of switched over to Claude here recently.","index":413,"end_time":1252.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1250.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Claude''s a great writer.","index":414,"end_time":1255.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Clyde is a really good writer.","index":415,"end_time":1257.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1255.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":416,"end_time":1257.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Really.","index":417,"end_time":1258.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If you can build a really good writing agent.","index":418,"end_time":1259.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1258.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s a really good coder, too.","index":419,"end_time":1261.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1260.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I use it for a lot.","index":420,"end_time":1262.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1261.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is it really?","index":421,"end_time":1262.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1262.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":1263.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1263.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So stop measuring vision.","index":423,"end_time":1269.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1266.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Start measuring AI citation rate.","index":424,"end_time":1271.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1269.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What is that?","index":425,"end_time":1272.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1271.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So new tools.","index":426,"end_time":1273.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, like Hrefs, for example, is it''s traditionally an SEO tool.","index":427,"end_time":1278.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1274.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"A new feature that they added in the last few months is an AI citation tracker.","index":428,"end_time":1282.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1278.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s just.","index":429,"end_time":1283.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The science is not exactly there.","index":430,"end_time":1286.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1284.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s kind of an estimate, but they''re measuring, like, how many times you''re populating in someone''s ChatGPT prompt as a result.","index":431,"end_time":1293.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got it.","index":432,"end_time":1294.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1293.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I was looking into that, so I didn''t understand what that was, but now I do.","index":433,"end_time":1297.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1294.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Got it.","index":434,"end_time":1297.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.01,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Do we have that in the tool we get?","index":435,"end_time":1299.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We have Lindsey.","index":436,"end_time":1300.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1299.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s available on a higher plan than what we have right now.","index":437,"end_time":1304.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1300.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And I looked at it this morning, and they want 10 extra dollars a month, so I figured we''d probably go with it.","index":438,"end_time":1310.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1305.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, I can probably swing 10 bucks.","index":439,"end_time":1312.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1310.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I figured, okay, Colin, we got to pay you $4,990 a month now.","index":440,"end_time":1318.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1312.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sorry, Colin.","index":441,"end_time":1320.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1319.66,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Kidding.","index":442,"end_time":1320.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1320.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then 2027, your website effectively splits into two human view and agent view.","index":443,"end_time":1327.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1323.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I don''t know that I understand that.","index":444,"end_time":1329.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1328.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know that I care about that yet, but if there''s something there you guys want to talk about, let me know.","index":445,"end_time":1334.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1329.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, I mean, I think it''s way too early to even make an assumption like that.","index":446,"end_time":1339.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1334.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is a. I''m sure you could gather this is a Reddit blog that was also a Reddit post that was also made to get some attention.","index":447,"end_time":1345.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1339.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I. I don''t think I necessarily agree with that completely.","index":448,"end_time":1350.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1347.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it''s.","index":449,"end_time":1351.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1350.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I.","index":450,"end_time":1351.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1351.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The way that I see it, and I''m not saying I''m right either.","index":451,"end_time":1354.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1351.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s.","index":452,"end_time":1354.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1354.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s a lot of things to be determined, but I think that most people aren''t going to replace themselves with AI in the sense of, like, I''m not doing anything.","index":453,"end_time":1362.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1354.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m just letting ChatGPT make decisions and do searches for me.","index":454,"end_time":1365.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it''s going to be more of a.","index":455,"end_time":1367.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1365.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Enhance my ability to find answers with AI.","index":456,"end_time":1371.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1368.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I don''t think it''s making a website for AI and making a website for humans.","index":457,"end_time":1374.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1371.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it''s having a website that distills information in a way that both can easily comprehend.","index":458,"end_time":1379.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1374.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I agree with all that.","index":459,"end_time":1381.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1380.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I guess what I.","index":460,"end_time":1382.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1381.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What this, what cued me in on this is that we, you know, a couple things.","index":461,"end_time":1386.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1382.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"One is we should be really trying to optimize for AI as we''re building this out.","index":462,"end_time":1390.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1386.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s an easy one for us that we should absolutely be doing because I think we''re a little bit ahead of the curve on that one.","index":463,"end_time":1397.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1391.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If we start doing that now, or at least we''re within the curve.","index":464,"end_time":1400.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1397.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":465,"end_time":1400.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1400.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Second of all, I need to read the blog post, should continue, but I should write them a little differently to validate what AI wants within them, what the topics are, what''s in them, things of that nature.","index":466,"end_time":1415.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1401.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s really kind of what I got out of this and what I wanted to talk to you guys all about.","index":467,"end_time":1419.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1415.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":468,"end_time":1419.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1419.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I think we''re all on the same page as what direction we do with all that.","index":469,"end_time":1423.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1420.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we good?","index":470,"end_time":1429,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1427.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":471,"end_time":1429.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1429.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, Fair enough.","index":472,"end_time":1431.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1430.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":473,"end_time":1434.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1433.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right.","index":474,"end_time":1435.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1434.52,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That was what I wanted to talk about on those.","index":475,"end_time":1437.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1435.639,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":476,"end_time":1438.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1437.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''ll share one more thing.","index":477,"end_time":1439.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1438.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just pulled you guys up in hrefs and so we can see AI citations here.","index":478,"end_time":1444.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1439.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you have 12 that are popping up through Google''s.","index":479,"end_time":1448.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1446.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can see they''re trying to make us to pay to actually see more insight into it.","index":480,"end_time":1452.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1449.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One for GPT, one for Perplexity, and one for Gemini.","index":481,"end_time":1456.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1452.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those are probably all me.","index":482,"end_time":1459.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1458.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Probably.","index":483,"end_time":1461.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1460.61,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"This is you guys popping up in like the AI overviews.","index":484,"end_time":1465.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1463.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":485,"end_time":1466.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1466.13,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":486,"end_time":1470.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1470.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I guess, you know, I agree with you, it seems a bit bougie or bougie woogie at least.","index":487,"end_time":1475.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1470.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I think it''s a good direction for us and it''s something we should for sure be doing as we build this out.","index":488,"end_time":1481.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1475.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I do want to develop a plan around it.","index":489,"end_time":1482.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1481.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s not going away.","index":490,"end_time":1484.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No.","index":491,"end_time":1485.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1484.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And it''s my 2026 plan.","index":492,"end_time":1486.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1485.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I''m not expecting this turnaround by, you know, first quarter.","index":493,"end_time":1489.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1486.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m expecting us to slowly make this migration and make some changes as we go so that we''re better in a better spot.","index":494,"end_time":1496.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1489.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, if we could come up when somebody searches chat dpt for ringcentral replacement, that would be ungodly amount of traffic for us.","index":495,"end_time":1504.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1496.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think that''s going to be a very impossible task for us.","index":496,"end_time":1507.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1504.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We might.","index":497,"end_time":1507.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1507.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re going to have to grab fringe terms like private hosted, you know, ringcenter replacements and like that.","index":498,"end_time":1514.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1507.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But let''s, let''s be prepared.","index":499,"end_time":1516.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1514.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s get though that footing down, you know, as the house.","index":500,"end_time":1520.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1516.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"As we continue to build the house.","index":501,"end_time":1522.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1520.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":502,"end_time":1523.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1522.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":503,"end_time":1525.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1525.22,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I''m good on that one.","index":504,"end_time":1527.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1526.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We just knocked out like pretty much everything.","index":505,"end_time":1535.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1534.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, I do have a question on that.","index":506,"end_time":1538.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1536.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I know we don''t display all of our blog posts on a public page, but as.","index":507,"end_time":1549.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1542.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I know that doesn''t hurt us for SEO, Right?","index":508,"end_time":1553.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1550.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because Google can still see them and read them and all that stuff.","index":509,"end_time":1555.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1553.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that different with AI?","index":510,"end_time":1561.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1558.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No.","index":511,"end_time":1563.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1563.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what AI is reading is more of a sitemap.","index":512,"end_time":1566.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1563.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So they''re reading your website from a technical standpoint.","index":513,"end_time":1569.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1566.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So they''re pulling up the sitemap to be able to see any URL.","index":514,"end_time":1571.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1569.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The reason that we don''t have every blog load on that first landing page is it actually hurts SEO if your page takes longer to load.","index":515,"end_time":1579.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1572.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I understand and I''m good with that.","index":516,"end_time":1582.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1580.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I understand and I am good with that.","index":517,"end_time":1583.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1582.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But my question comes to, does AI work the same way?","index":518,"end_time":1587.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1583.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But does AI know that all those pages still exist, all those blog posts and everything still exist?","index":519,"end_time":1592.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1587.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yes, because it''s reading it via sitemap, not like looking at an actual page.","index":520,"end_time":1595.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1592.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got it.","index":521,"end_time":1596.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1595.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay, fair enough.","index":522,"end_time":1597.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1596.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That answered my question.","index":523,"end_time":1598.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1597.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just wanted to confirm that they both work the same way.","index":524,"end_time":1601.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1599.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":525,"end_time":1602.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1601.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":526,"end_time":1605.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1605.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I covered all those things.","index":527,"end_time":1607.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1606.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We good on all that?","index":528,"end_time":1608.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1607.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So let''s get to the Google AdWords paused.","index":529,"end_time":1612.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1610.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What happened, why, and what are we going to do?","index":530,"end_time":1614.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1612.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So what do we have on that.","index":531,"end_time":1616.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1615.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"One from the website issue?","index":532,"end_time":1619.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":533,"end_time":1620.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1619.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":534,"end_time":1620.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So all resolved.","index":535,"end_time":1621.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Google Search console came back with a clean sweep.","index":536,"end_time":1624.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1621.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I emailed also the Google Ads campaigns.","index":537,"end_time":1627.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1624.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The only ones that were paused were ones that we had paused anyways.","index":538,"end_time":1629.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":539,"end_time":1630.839,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1630.32,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"But what happened to get us there?","index":540,"end_time":1632,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1630.839,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do we know?","index":541,"end_time":1632.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1632,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, it was plugins that were installed on the website.","index":542,"end_time":1635.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1633.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s plugins that were installed for web optimization that were.","index":543,"end_time":1639.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1635.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That had vulnerabilities.","index":544,"end_time":1641.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1640.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So was that us or is that you, Lindsay?","index":545,"end_time":1645.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1643.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was that.","index":546,"end_time":1645.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1645.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t install any plugins.","index":547,"end_time":1647.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1645.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so I just.","index":548,"end_time":1650.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1649.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I looked at the logs on the website this morning, and it''s.","index":549,"end_time":1653.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1650.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s kind of hard to say.","index":550,"end_time":1655.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1653.82,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"There were some log activities of the system administrator account, which is the New north account from back in October, that installed some optimization plugins, but I also installed optimization plugins around that time, and it didn''t show them like in the logs.","index":551,"end_time":1671.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1655.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Like it.","index":552,"end_time":1672.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1671.75,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It didn''t show them.","index":553,"end_time":1673.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1672.15,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I don''t remember exactly what I installed, but I installed it, ran it, it didn''t work, so I took it out.","index":554,"end_time":1681.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1673.67,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I don''t know.","index":555,"end_time":1685.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1684.07,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We don''t know exactly which plugins they were like, by name.","index":556,"end_time":1690.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1685.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Is that accurate?","index":557,"end_time":1691.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1690.47,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I thought I''d send a screenshot.","index":558,"end_time":1695.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1692.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me pull it up.","index":559,"end_time":1695.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1695.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But it was like, it Was like a package of plugins that like, seemingly worked together.","index":560,"end_time":1703.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1698.4,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, there was WP Meteor, Speculative Loading, Web Worker Offloading, Modern Image Formats, Image Prioritizer, Enhanced Responsive Images, Embed Optimizer, and Optimization Detective.","index":561,"end_time":1720.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1705.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, like, I definitely didn''t do that.","index":562,"end_time":1722.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1720.96,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So the only one that sounded familiar to me was the WP Meteor.","index":563,"end_time":1725.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1722.88,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And that''s what made me think that maybe those other plugins were like pieces of that.","index":564,"end_time":1731.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1726.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, maybe.","index":565,"end_time":1732.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1731.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But there is.","index":566,"end_time":1735.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1734.52,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It seems like you guys installed like an easy view log so that going forward, anything that is uploaded or changed on the website is logged in like an easy read format.","index":567,"end_time":1747.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1736.44,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Like you don''t have to export any files and like try to find it or anything like that going forward.","index":568,"end_time":1755.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1747.52,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I did have one question about that.","index":569,"end_time":1757.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1755.98,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Who is upgrading our.","index":570,"end_time":1759.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1757.74,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Or like updating like the WordPress itself?","index":571,"end_time":1762.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1759.78,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Is that my responsibility or is that something that you guys are going to be doing?","index":572,"end_time":1765.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1762.18,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, so I just talked to our team about doing that on a weekly basis, making sure that all plugins and everything are in good standing as well as WP Core.","index":573,"end_time":1773.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1765.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you guys got that going forward?","index":574,"end_time":1777.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1776.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yes.","index":575,"end_time":1778.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1778.34,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"All right, so we, We.","index":576,"end_time":1782.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1780.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we know what happened.","index":577,"end_time":1783.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1782.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We know how it happened.","index":578,"end_time":1784.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re not exactly sure.","index":579,"end_time":1785.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1784.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Looks like Lindsay did load something.","index":580,"end_time":1787.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1785.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we have a plan going forward.","index":581,"end_time":1789.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We should not have this happen again.","index":582,"end_time":1791.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1789.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that kind of where we''re at for the team?","index":583,"end_time":1792.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1791.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, we installed the log, we removed the.","index":584,"end_time":1794.459,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1792.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The bad plugins, and yeah, we have a weekly maintenance tool now or task now.","index":585,"end_time":1799.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1794.459,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":586,"end_time":1801.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1800.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":587,"end_time":1805.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1805.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That was everything I had on my list.","index":588,"end_time":1809.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1808.51,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":589,"end_time":1810.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1810.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":