verified now.","index":604,"end_time":1845.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1840.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yep.","index":605,"end_time":1845.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1845.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Saw that.","index":606,"end_time":1846.159,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1845.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":607,"end_time":1846.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1846.159,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":608,"end_time":1847.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1847.28,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That was a huge pain in the ass.","index":609,"end_time":1849.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1848.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Dude.","index":610,"end_time":1851.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1851.44,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"They''re the worst.","index":611,"end_time":1852.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1851.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They''re like, I got.","index":612,"end_time":1853.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1852.56,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I got the documents and they''re like, oh, we don''t want it.","index":613,"end_time":1855.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1853.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And a PDF.","index":614,"end_time":1857.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1855.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We want it in a Word doc.","index":615,"end_time":1858.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1857.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m like, what?","index":616,"end_time":1860.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1858.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, tell me that''s the most Microsoft thing ever.","index":617,"end_time":1862.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1860.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Seriously, that''s crazy.","index":618,"end_time":1865.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1862.73,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, we realize PDF is internationally the standard, but, you know, you got to upload it As a word doc.","index":619,"end_time":1871.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1865.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because we''re Microsoft and we''re dicks.","index":620,"end_time":1874.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1872.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Crazy.","index":621,"end_time":1875.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1874.81,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I think that''s all I have for awesome.","index":622,"end_time":1880.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1877.05,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"This meeting.","index":623,"end_time":1881.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1880.53,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"When do we.","index":624,"end_time":1881.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1881.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I know you have to send me the page, but have we built out the campaign yet at all?","index":625,"end_time":1885.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1881.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we have it all built in our notes.","index":626,"end_time":1886.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1885.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We just have to, like actually paste it into the account now that it''s verified.","index":627,"end_time":1889.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1886.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":628,"end_time":1891.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1891.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":629,"end_time":1893.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1892.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, get that page over.","index":630,"end_time":1894.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1893.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Then we''ll try to get it approved so next week we can talk a little bit more about getting that active.","index":631,"end_time":1897.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1894.35,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":632,"end_time":1898.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1898.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I am extremely curious to see how that plays out.","index":633,"end_time":1901.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1898.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yes, we are as well.","index":634,"end_time":1902.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1901.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you guys do any advertising there today for anybody?","index":635,"end_time":1906.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1903.35,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Not for any of my clients currently at this agency.","index":636,"end_time":1911.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1908.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"At the last agency, we did more Bing.","index":637,"end_time":1913.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1911.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You guys sell like, arthritis medicine and shit there?","index":638,"end_time":1917.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1915.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, it''s not arthritis medicine.","index":639,"end_time":1920.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1918.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was.","index":640,"end_time":1920.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1920.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s a lot of different things.","index":641,"end_time":1922.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1920.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For those.","index":642,"end_time":1925.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1924.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"For us old people.","index":643,"end_time":1926.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1925.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I say that as somebody who''s freaking.","index":644,"end_time":1928.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1926.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"One of the companies was in producing medical equipment for, like, elderly patients.","index":645,"end_time":1936.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1929.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They would make like, the gels and stuff that go into operating rooms and like the table pads and things like that is very niche.","index":646,"end_time":1944.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1937.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":647,"end_time":1947.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1946.75,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":648,"end_time":1950.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1949.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, well, if anything else pops up, please do let me know.","index":649,"end_time":1952.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1950.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, I''ll write some new headlines.","index":650,"end_time":1954.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1952.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m back to back until 6pm tonight, so I''ll get back to you guys later.","index":651,"end_time":1957.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1954.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, follow up with this.","index":652,"end_time":1960.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1957.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":653,"end_time":1961.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1961.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":654,"end_time":1962.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1962.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, thank you guys and hope everyone feels better.","index":655,"end_time":1965.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1962.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":656,"end_time":1966.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1966.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":657,"end_time":1967.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1966.57,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Bye.","index":658,"end_time":1967.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1967.29,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"}],"dateString":"2026-01-06T19:30:00.000Z","host_email":"mlook@techmode.com","meeting_link":"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meetin