    '{"id":"01KDDPEG2ZYKXCCYY4B526N2JP","title":"AQI // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Integration and Data Management**\n\nThe team is finalizing the contact sync between **HubSpot and Salesforce** to ensure clean, accurate data before activating the integration (01:28).\n\n- **Contact numbers are being refined** from an initial **29,000 contacts** based on filters, aiming to narrow down to relevant prospects and customers (01:58).\n- Colin emphasized consolidating and monitoring fields rather than deleting immediately, proposing a **30-day observation period** to identify necessary fields before full migration (03:21).\n- Vivian recommended involving Kyle’s team after the monitoring period for clean-up decisions, reflecting a cautious change management approach (03:55).\n- The integration includes finalized workflows with **Zoom and Eventbrite**, ensuring webinar registrations flow accurately into HubSpot with automated emails and tagging (04:48).\n\n## **Newsletter and Campaign Automation**\n\nA modular **newsletter template** was developed in HubSpot to support multiple campaign types, including quarterly product newsletters for **Aquatic Informatics** and **HawkWims**, with flexible branding options (05:54).\n\n- Vivian requested prominent product branding placement, such as logos side-by-side in the hero section, to reflect the company’s product-led approach (07:07).\n- The team confirmed eight water quality company logos are included, aligning with the number listed on the Veralto site, with flexibility to add or remove logos as needed (08:42).\n- Automation of webinar registration ownership was prioritized to assign new contacts to the correct marketing owner, avoiding manual workload as contact numbers scale (27:35).\n- Barb plans multiple monthly campaigns, treating each event and webinar as separate campaigns, with workflows to be tested and validated over Q1 (13:00).\n\n## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Strategy**\n\nABM infrastructure is being updated with detailed documentation outlining contact criteria, communication channels, and integration points, enabling clarity and transparency for current and future team members (15:34).\n\n- Barb clarified that **29,000 contacts** represent combined general contact criteria, while ABM has separate, specific criteria for targeting (16:18).\n- Colin highlighted key foundational inputs needed: **communication owners** (e.g., company head, sales lead) and **irresistible offers** such as ROI calculators or competitor benchmark analyses to drive engagement (18:10).\n- Two distinct ABM programs will run separately for **Aquarius** and **HawkWims**, with infrastructure and documentation reflecting this split (20:13).\n- Vivian is collaborating with internal teams on personas, messaging, and content to align ABM setup with actual customer needs and reduce guesswork in campaign building (17:31).\n\n## **Performance Reporting and Lead Scoring**\n\nA comprehensive **performance reporting plan** built around DataBox and HubSpot metrics is underway, designed to track customer journeys, lifecycle stages, and campaign effectiveness (21:30).\n\n- Colin confirmed the plan includes lead scoring but requires updated touchpoint values from Barb’s team to reflect the current system accurately (22:08).\n- Barb will resend lead scoring details to ensure the framework includes new touchpoints without changing the overall scoring scale of 100 (23:14).\n- DataBox supports flexible date comparisons like month-over-month and year-over-year, helping measure traffic and engagement trends (25:34).\n- A **company-level website visitor tracking tool** costing **$600/month** was proposed for detailed account insights, pending internal discussion (24:38).\n- Access to **AQI LinkedIn Ads account** is needed to track lead generation form completion rates, with Barb committing to provide access promptly (26:37).\n\n## **Webinar and Nurture Campaign Tracking**\n\nWebinar workflows are set up with automated emails for registration, attendance, and on-demand video follow-ups, with three webinars scheduled this month for smooth execution (20:56).\n\n- Barb emphasized the importance of communication around form cutovers, especially for the Hawk referral forms that feed **20% of sales opportunities**, to avoid disruption (14:26).\n- Nurture campaigns are tracked in HubSpot, capturing metrics like MQLs and SQLs, but further work is planned to isolate nurture’s contribution relative to other channels (28:52).\n- Vivian noted the strategic value of measuring nurture impact on conversions, hypothesizing nurture drives a significant portion of MQLs beyond paid channels (30:13).\n- Colin explained that while full multi-touch attribution needs a larger budget, initial first- and last-touch attribution can be implemented to better understand channel influence (31:07).\n\n## **Timelines, Collaboration, and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is on track to complete workflow setups and integrations in early Q1, with a key meeting scheduled with Nicole on Monday to finalize contact data filtering (09:57).\n\n- Vivian requested a **30-minute session** to explore DataBox functionality before the **Sales Kickoff event on January 21**, ensuring readiness to present insights (10:38).\n- Barb will prepare the AQI marketing team on DataBox ahead of that event, while Colin offered ongoing support for training and troubleshooting (11:07).\n- Colin acknowledged the extensive work done in just over two months, with Barb recommending HubSpot migration to Hawk’s IT team, signaling a strong business endorsement (32:30).\n- Continuous updates to documentation and campaign plans will maintain alignment, with Colin emphasizing transparency and ease of onboarding for future team members (23:40).","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot Integration","Salesforce Sync","Data Box Dashboard","ABM Strategy","Webinar Workflows","Lead Scoring Framework"],"overview":"- **Contact Sync Process:** Finalizing HubSpot and Salesforce integration; refining contacts from 29,000 to targeted prospects. \n- **Newsletter Automation:** Modular templates allow flexible branding for different campaigns, highlighting multiple product logos to enhance visibility. \n- **ABM Strategy Update:** New documentation clarifies contact criteria and communication channels, focusing on engaging offers for targeted outreach. \n- **Performance Reporting Plan:** Developing comprehensive tracking around customer journeys; lead scoring needs updated touchpoints for accuracy. \n- **Webinar Engagement:** Automated workflows established for webinars, enhancing communication, and tracking nurture campaigns'' effectiveness on MQLs. \n- **Upcoming Milestones:** Workflow setups expected early Q1; training session on DataBox scheduled for readiness before January 21 event.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nSchedule meeting with Nicole for Monday to finalize integration details (10:02)\nShare calendar with Vivian for Data Box training sessions and coordinate 30-minute prep session before Sales Kickoff event (11:50)\nSend performance reporting plan document to the team for review (22:08)\nUpdate HubSpot workflows to automate webinar registration owner assignment (28:00)\n\n**Barb Willans**\nConnect with Nicole for contact filtering and finalize data sync with Salesforce (02:12)\nResend updated lead scoring framework document to team (23:14)\nPrepare and send email notifications for form cutovers affecting referral forms to marketing and sales teams (15:25)\nMeet Claudia to confirm Eventbrite capture of webinar registrations (13:55)\nDecide on purchase or further discussion regarding IP-based company tracking platform for website visitors (25:24)\nProvide instructions to Barb for adding Marketers In Demand as partner on LinkedIn ads account (26:30)\n\n**Vivian Chan**\nCoordinate with Barb to schedule meeting with Nicole and assist in onboarding new coordinator for product newsletter management (10:02)\nParticipate in discussions on ABM foundational content including personas, messaging, and offers (18:00)\nPrepare to socialize and present Data Box insights to marketing team (11:50)\nFollow-up on nurture campaign impact metrics development and report back with insights (29:48)\n"},"duration":33.650001525878906,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Vivian Chan"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"Barb Willans"},{"id":3,"name":"Colin Costigan"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Sick.","index":0,"end_time":0.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.08,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like not too like.","index":1,"end_time":1.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":0.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just.","index":2,"end_time":2.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.68,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s not bad sick.","index":3,"end_time":3.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2.12,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s just sick for a long time.","index":4,"end_time":5.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.44,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Sick.","index":5,"end_time":5.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":5.2,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Just lingering.","index":6,"end_time":7.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":6.32,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Lingering.","index":7,"end_time":8.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.6,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, I totally get that.","index":8,"end_time":12.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":8.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve.","index":9,"end_time":12.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":12.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My wife and I were like joking with each other this morning.","index":10,"end_time":14.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":12.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve gotten worse every day.","index":11,"end_time":15.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":14.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But luckily our daughter''s getting better, so.","index":12,"end_time":17.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":15.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":13,"end_time":18.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":17.68,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Good.","index":14,"end_time":19.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":19.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":15,"end_time":21.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":20.72,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Hi, Gay.","index":16,"end_time":22.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":21.84,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Happy New Year.","index":17,"end_time":23.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":22.72,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Happy New Year.","index":18,"end_time":24.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hello and thank you for my hat.","index":19,"end_time":30.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":25.36,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I love it.","index":20,"end_time":34.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":33.27,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, thanks.","index":21,"end_time":35.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":34.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a car heart.","index":22,"end_time":36.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":35.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hopefully it''s comfy.","index":23,"end_time":37.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":36.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know my little mug here.","index":24,"end_time":39.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":37.83,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So much appreciated.","index":25,"end_time":41.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":39.67,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Of course.","index":26,"end_time":42.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":42.07,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":27,"end_time":43.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":43.19,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"New Year''s Eve, Canada Post.","index":28,"end_time":47.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":45.11,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''m like, what?","index":29,"end_time":47.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":47.03,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So, yeah, no, I really appreciate it.","index":30,"end_time":49.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":47.91,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":31,"end_time":50.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":49.79,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Of course.","index":32,"end_time":50.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":50.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":33,"end_time":51.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":51.11,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All right, well, I know we have a lot to cover today, so I''ll pull up my slide deck.","index":34,"end_time":54.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":52.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Barb, if there''s anything that you wanted to start with, obviously, please go ahead.","index":35,"end_time":58.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":54.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For sure you got what I sent last night.","index":36,"end_time":61.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":58.72,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Sorry, it was last minute so I don''t expect you to have all the answers.","index":37,"end_time":65.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":61.68,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But yeah, it was quite the list.","index":38,"end_time":66.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":65.04,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Well then I''ll be glad that we can happily surprise you.","index":39,"end_time":70.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so yeah, quite a packed agenda.","index":40,"end_time":74.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":71.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll go over just things from Q4 that were accomplished priorities and focus for Q1.","index":41,"end_time":80.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":74.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then we''ll go through ABM webinar databox.","index":42,"end_time":83.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":80.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Box and the newsletter template.","index":43,"end_time":85.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect, thank you.","index":44,"end_time":87.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.22,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All right.","index":45,"end_time":88.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":88.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So Barb, this is kind of.","index":46,"end_time":90.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":88.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In your emails alluded to this that you had spoken to the head of.","index":47,"end_time":94.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":91.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I believe it was whims but not Aquarius or maybe I have that backwards of getting the exact contact numbers and filters.","index":48,"end_time":101.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":95.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that is pretty much where we''re at of finalizing the sync between the two systems of HubSpot and Salesforce.","index":49,"end_time":107.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":101.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So as soon as we have that like this is the number of contacts as a source of truth, then we are in a good spot to set up that integration.","index":50,"end_time":116.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":107.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Turn it on and make sure that everything maps correctly.","index":51,"end_time":118.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":116.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":52,"end_time":119.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":118.69,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":53,"end_time":119.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":119.33,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I sent over Jason, he was the head of sales and we''ll speak with Nicole this week.","index":54,"end_time":123.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":119.65,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So that should narrow down the 29,000 considerably to start with.","index":55,"end_time":128.129,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":123.53,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But yeah, that''s what you got is what Vivian and I discussed with him last week.","index":56,"end_time":132.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":128.129,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":57,"end_time":132.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":132.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, because I don''t know if it was last week or the week before last time we met.","index":58,"end_time":137.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":132.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know we went through and there''s just depending on which filters we activate inside of Salesforce, that number changes pretty drastically.","index":59,"end_time":143.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":137.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And of course we like to operate from clean data.","index":60,"end_time":146.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":144.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So as soon as we have that true number then we''re in a good spot pretty much just to Hit go on the integration.","index":61,"end_time":151.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":146.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":62,"end_time":152.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":152.31,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":63,"end_time":153.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":152.79,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":64,"end_time":154.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":153.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we have the mapping document, everything that we''ve shared.","index":65,"end_time":156.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":154.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We also have.","index":66,"end_time":157.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":156.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We did that form audit for you and there''s a lot of forms that have been inactive that were built between 2012 and 2018.","index":67,"end_time":163.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":157.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, just we''ve built several forms.","index":68,"end_time":168.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":165.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Obviously you and me and Guy have gone back and forth of HubSpot forms, especially webinar being a focus.","index":69,"end_time":173.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":168.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So feel great about those as well.","index":70,"end_time":175.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":173.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":71,"end_time":177.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":176.92,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So a question on those ones.","index":72,"end_time":179.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":177.48,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Is this an opportunity for us to share back the unused fields that marketing owns back to the Salesforce team and.","index":73,"end_time":187.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.48,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And clean them up?","index":74,"end_time":188.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":187.8,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Meaning it''s an opportunity.","index":75,"end_time":190.399,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.08,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like there are a couple of tabs that marketing owns and I suspect that half of those fields are no longer relevant.","index":76,"end_time":197.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":190.399,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Do we.","index":77,"end_time":198.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Do we go back and delete them in Salesforce?","index":78,"end_time":200.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.72,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":79,"end_time":202.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":201.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s two schools of approach to it And Barb, you''ll probably know where I''m going with this.","index":80,"end_time":206.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":202.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I like to like consolidate our list of fields that we''re managing.","index":81,"end_time":210.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":206.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not necessarily deleting them right away, but just saying this is our set list.","index":82,"end_time":214.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":210.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then watch it for it.","index":83,"end_time":217.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":215.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can depend on a period, usually about 30 days.","index":84,"end_time":219.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":217.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If any of those old fields are populating, figure out do we need that, should that go somewhere else or do we not need it at all?","index":85,"end_time":225.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":219.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we just fully move over to the new forms that marketing really truly needs.","index":86,"end_time":230.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":225.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, it''s to your point, Vivian.","index":87,"end_time":233.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":231.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a great opportunity to do so.","index":88,"end_time":235.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":233.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":89,"end_time":236.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So yeah, I like that approach.","index":90,"end_time":237.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.07,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Just to like be a little careful.","index":91,"end_time":240.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.67,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like let''s have a marker and then at that time, marker.","index":92,"end_time":243.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.31,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Then let''s bring in Kyle and team.","index":93,"end_time":247.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":244.23,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So yeah.","index":94,"end_time":248.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":247.67,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Great.","index":95,"end_time":248.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":248.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":96,"end_time":249.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":249.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":97,"end_time":251.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":250.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then we also built data box and I know we''ll go over that more in depth.","index":98,"end_time":255.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":251.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Barbara got the wishlist, so happy to go through that.","index":99,"end_time":257.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":255.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I know that you had a question on Riverside.","index":100,"end_time":261.249,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":259.249,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When I tested logging in on my phone, I didn''t get any issues.","index":101,"end_time":264.209,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":261.249,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know that you were experiencing some issues.","index":102,"end_time":266.289,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":264.369,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I don''t know if you want to just maybe connect offline for a couple minutes on that.","index":103,"end_time":270.369,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":266.609,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let''s connect offline.","index":104,"end_time":271.889,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":270.769,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I think I understand what I did.","index":105,"end_time":273.729,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":272.209,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I think I just have to delete my personal one and then reissue it.","index":106,"end_time":276.929,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":273.729,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":107,"end_time":277.969,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":277.249,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":108,"end_time":278.569,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":278.129,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So let me try that again today and then I''ll get it over to Viv with a loom video.","index":109,"end_time":282.609,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":278.569,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":110,"end_time":283.609,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":282.849,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you have any issues.","index":111,"end_time":284.449,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":283.609,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, happy to hop on few minute.","index":112,"end_time":286.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":284.529,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Call, whatever we need.","index":113,"end_time":287.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":286.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":114,"end_time":288.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":287.45,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"We have the integration set up between Zoom and HubSpot.","index":115,"end_time":291.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":288.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so all those forms have been updated.","index":116,"end_time":292.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":291.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Registrations to the webinars are filtering into HubSpot.","index":117,"end_time":296.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":293.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They are getting an email right now, Barb, that I sent you from Zoom when they register.","index":118,"end_time":300.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":296.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And they''re being correctly loaded and tagged into HubSpot events as well.","index":119,"end_time":304.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":301.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think there was even another one yesterday or the day before.","index":120,"end_time":308.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":305.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kevin something.","index":121,"end_time":309.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":308.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":122,"end_time":310.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":310.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":123,"end_time":312.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":312.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then also Eventbrite has been integrated fully.","index":124,"end_time":315.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":312.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Vivian, I''m not sure if you''ve.","index":125,"end_time":320.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":318.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Seen the newsletter template, but this is what we built as a modular approach.","index":126,"end_time":324.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":320.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So starting with a nice hero section here, then getting into news and the way that we build these, HubSpot has a drag and drop feature.","index":127,"end_time":334.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":326.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It doesn''t come out of the box with a bunch of really nice looking graphics.","index":128,"end_time":338.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":335.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we custom build modules and whether we are doing it, Barb is doing it, anyone else on the team, it is literally as easy as click on this, change image, change text, remove this entire section, everything like that.","index":129,"end_time":351.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":338.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":130,"end_time":352.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":352.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks good to me.","index":131,"end_time":355.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.79,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"The only feedback that I have is that, sorry, can you refresh me on the use case?","index":132,"end_time":362.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.87,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Because when I look at the use case, Barb and team, the one that''s in my head is we want to do a product newsletter that''s quarterly, that I would love the new coordinator to own.","index":133,"end_time":374.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":362.63,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And so one would be for Aquarius and one would be for hawkwims.","index":134,"end_time":377.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":374.35,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And because we are a product led company, meaning nobody knows our brand, we would just need somewhere to put in the Aquarius and Hawkwinds brand for that use case.","index":135,"end_time":390.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":378.35,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"This also might be a different newsletter for nurture.","index":136,"end_time":394.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.07,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So just wanted to check on that.","index":137,"end_time":396.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":394.47,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, so the way that we build it, it''s holistic.","index":138,"end_time":398.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":396.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":139,"end_time":399.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":398.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it can actually accomplish all of these things.","index":140,"end_time":401.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":399.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can just make like, we can make three versions, we can make 10 versions of this thing with just the content that we want to send out and that just Barb, on your cadence.","index":141,"end_time":409.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":401.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, we want to send a product newsletter every quarter.","index":142,"end_time":411.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":409.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We want to send an awareness email every month.","index":143,"end_time":414.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":411.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We want to send out a webinar email.","index":144,"end_time":416.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":414.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, whatever we need to do.","index":145,"end_time":417.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":416.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can just basically drag and drop out of this template and update that.","index":146,"end_time":420.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":417.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s perfect.","index":147,"end_time":423.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":422.87,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Can we go all the way up though?","index":148,"end_time":427.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":425.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, where would we put the product branding?","index":149,"end_time":429.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":427.03,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Because it would need to be up front and center.","index":150,"end_time":431.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":429.07,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":151,"end_time":432.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":432.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can replace anything in like this hero section.","index":152,"end_time":434.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":432.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can add even more spots for logos if we need it.","index":153,"end_time":437.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":434.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think, I think it''s like an aquatic informatics logo on the left and then the Product logo on the right.","index":154,"end_time":443.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.26,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So I think it''s as simple as that.","index":155,"end_time":444.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":443.06,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":156,"end_time":444.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":444.34,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, we can do that.","index":157,"end_time":445.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":444.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, no problem at all.","index":158,"end_time":447.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":159,"end_time":448.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":447.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, no, no issues with this template.","index":160,"end_time":450.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":448.34,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":161,"end_time":451.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":450.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We just need to put it to use and then.","index":162,"end_time":453.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I think it''s solid.","index":163,"end_time":456.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":454.1,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":164,"end_time":456.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":456.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other question I had is that we put in the other water quality companies at the very bottom of Royalta water quality companies.","index":165,"end_time":465.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.89,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"What was the thinking behind that?","index":166,"end_time":470.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those are just our designers taking content from the website.","index":167,"end_time":472.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":470.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can forego this section.","index":168,"end_time":474.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":472.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can switch around the logos if we want to.","index":169,"end_time":477.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":474.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have the Hawk Loco down here, for example, or Aquarius wimp, you know, whatever we want to do.","index":170,"end_time":482.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":477.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or if we want to just get.","index":171,"end_time":483.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":482.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Rid of it, we can.","index":172,"end_time":483.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":483.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I need to think about this one because it''s not as simple as just having it there first.","index":173,"end_time":490.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":486.86,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I think we''ve got 10 water quality companies and if we omit two.","index":174,"end_time":496.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":490.86,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I think we''re missing one of them.","index":175,"end_time":499.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":496.38,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like, that one will be like, why did you not include us?","index":176,"end_time":502.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":499.98,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Right, so it''s missing one logo for sure.","index":177,"end_time":505.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":503.02,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And then I like the spirit of it.","index":178,"end_time":511.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.06,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s like, hey, go check out the other.","index":179,"end_time":513.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":511.35,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Our other brothers and sisters.","index":180,"end_time":515.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":513.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I don''t mind it.","index":181,"end_time":518.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":517.11,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I don''t mind it, actually.","index":182,"end_time":524.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":183,"end_time":524.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.23,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I think it''s just missing logos.","index":184,"end_time":525.789,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.55,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So if you go to Veralto and under water quality count the logos, there''s.","index":185,"end_time":529.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":525.789,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"There''s 10 companies.","index":186,"end_time":530.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.39,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"There should be.","index":187,"end_time":531.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":530.23,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":188,"end_time":532.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If I''m not mistaken, but maybe I''ve counted wrong.","index":189,"end_time":535.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.71,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So, yeah, under our companies, let''s see how many are there?","index":190,"end_time":540.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":535.03,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I always think there''s 10.","index":191,"end_time":541.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.26,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So it could be me.","index":192,"end_time":542.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.42,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Explore water quality.","index":193,"end_time":544.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":542.82,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Is it just eight?","index":194,"end_time":545.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":544.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One, two, three, four, five, six.","index":195,"end_time":550.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, it''s eight.","index":196,"end_time":551.539,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":550.82,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s just eight.","index":197,"end_time":552.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":551.539,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, we''re fine.","index":198,"end_time":552.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re fine.","index":199,"end_time":553.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":552.98,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Cool.","index":200,"end_time":554.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":553.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And the way that we''ll build that, we can.","index":201,"end_time":556.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":554.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll just have a module so you can just say like add or remove any image specifically.","index":202,"end_time":561.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":556.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, sounds great.","index":203,"end_time":562.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":561.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s eight.","index":204,"end_time":563.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":562.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not ten, it''s me.","index":205,"end_time":564.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":563.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, well, we will get this.","index":206,"end_time":566.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":565.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Built into HubSpot then.","index":207,"end_time":567.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":566.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":208,"end_time":569.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":209,"end_time":569.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":569.31,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":210,"end_time":570.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":570.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, Barb, I know you also wanted to just go over this slide and kind of talk about where we''re at.","index":211,"end_time":575.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":571.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, as per the timeline, we are right here at the beginning of January.","index":212,"end_time":579.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":575.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we are in the midst of workflow, set up a migration, and again, we''re pretty much just waiting on the number of contacts to finalize the integration and then any additional workflows beyond what we''ve already set up.","index":213,"end_time":590.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":579.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Between HubSpot and Zoom and Eventbrite and all of the other integrations as well.","index":214,"end_time":594.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":590.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds great.","index":215,"end_time":596.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":596.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":216,"end_time":597.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":597.48,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Go ahead, Barb.","index":217,"end_time":599.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":597.88,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Do we want to.","index":218,"end_time":599.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.12,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Do you want me to put on schedule a meeting with Nicole on Monday?","index":219,"end_time":602.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.76,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"She''ll be back.","index":220,"end_time":603.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":602.76,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I was just going to ask you that exact thing.","index":221,"end_time":605.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":603.32,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''m like, can we meet with Nicole on Monday?","index":222,"end_time":607.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":605.32,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s do that.","index":223,"end_time":609,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":607.96,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay, I will do that right now.","index":224,"end_time":611.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":609.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, Vivian, we also added in just a note here, you.","index":225,"end_time":615.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":611.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Barb had mentioned you were doing a socialization of sharing the data box slides with the team.","index":226,"end_time":621.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":615.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I didn''t know if there''s any.","index":227,"end_time":622.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":621.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you wanted to meet and go through how to talk through those or change any of the filters or anything like that.","index":228,"end_time":628.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":623.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll go a little bit more into data box in this conversation, but if you wanted to have any additional time to go through that, we are more.","index":229,"end_time":634.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":628.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Than happy to do that.","index":230,"end_time":635.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":634.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t totally understand what the additional time would be.","index":231,"end_time":641.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":638.07,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Just anytime that if you wanted to prep for when you''re socializing this to the AQI team, like, here''s how to talk through data box.","index":232,"end_time":650.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":643.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you have any questions.","index":233,"end_time":652.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''d probably be good to have 30 minutes.","index":234,"end_time":656.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":652.75,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like to let me play with it once we''ve got the final.","index":235,"end_time":659.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":656.83,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And then I''m.","index":236,"end_time":661.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.59,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I always inevitably have questions, so that would be great.","index":237,"end_time":664.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":661.43,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":238,"end_time":665.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":664.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But with that said, Barb, I want you to prep the AQI marketing team on it as well.","index":239,"end_time":673.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.15,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":240,"end_time":674.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":673.76,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Oh, I can prep the marketing team for sure.","index":241,"end_time":676.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":674.52,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, I''d love to.","index":242,"end_time":678.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":676.88,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I can''t wait for that green.","index":243,"end_time":679.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":678.04,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That was for.","index":244,"end_time":680.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":680.12,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And I can never remember the name of the event you''re going to on the 21st or that week.","index":245,"end_time":685.719,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":680.88,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And that''s why we put it in there.","index":246,"end_time":687.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":685.96,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Is because you''re in front of everybody.","index":247,"end_time":690.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.8,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I''ll do the marketing team, but you have a seat, group of people.","index":248,"end_time":694.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":691.08,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"This is cko.","index":249,"end_time":696.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.59,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"This is a sales kickoff.","index":250,"end_time":697.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":696.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":251,"end_time":698.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":698.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":252,"end_time":701.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":700.95,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And I do need to know the data box by then, so thank you for that reminder.","index":253,"end_time":704.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":701.31,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":254,"end_time":705.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":704.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":255,"end_time":706.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":705.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, well, we''ll reach out.","index":256,"end_time":707.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":706.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll share our calendar, and you can just book anytime that works for you.","index":257,"end_time":710.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":707.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":258,"end_time":711.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":710.47,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And when will the data box.","index":259,"end_time":712.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":711.109,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Is it ready already?","index":260,"end_time":713.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":712.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":261,"end_time":713.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":713.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll show some updates that we made based on the email that Barb sent over.","index":262,"end_time":716.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":713.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re still working through a few of them just because they require a custom build for, like, the event registrations, et cetera.","index":263,"end_time":721.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":716.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, sounds great.","index":264,"end_time":723.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":721.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":265,"end_time":724.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Barb, is there anything else on here.","index":266,"end_time":725.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":724.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That you wanted to go through for this timeline?","index":267,"end_time":726.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":725.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":268,"end_time":727.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":727.45,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"This looks amazing.","index":269,"end_time":728.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":727.77,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And I just.","index":270,"end_time":730.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":728.53,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I knew you were going to say it, but it just.","index":271,"end_time":732.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":730.17,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I need a hobby or something.","index":272,"end_time":733.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":732.41,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Because as soon as you said, yeah, we''re on track and we''re cutting over, I''m like, ha.","index":273,"end_time":737.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":733.85,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yes.","index":274,"end_time":738.729,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.249,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And this is a huge amount of work team.","index":275,"end_time":743.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.77,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So thank you so much, you guys.","index":276,"end_time":744.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.05,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Really, really.","index":277,"end_time":747.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":745.69,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, You''ve made it go really smoothly given the vast amount of decisions that we''ve had to make.","index":278,"end_time":752.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.85,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So that''s how we like to operate.","index":279,"end_time":754.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":752.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s great to hear.","index":280,"end_time":755.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":754.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":281,"end_time":755.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":755.47,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":282,"end_time":756.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":283,"end_time":757.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":757.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, Barb, I know this was just kind of a slide you wanted to throw in as well.","index":284,"end_time":761.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":757.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just talking about different priorities in Q1 and making sure that we''re aligned to any internal conversations you guys have been having.","index":285,"end_time":767.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":761.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m sure, you know, with it being the new year, you guys probably in budgeting conversations and how do we want to attack the market?","index":286,"end_time":773.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":767.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What channels do we want to use?","index":287,"end_time":774.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":773.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just want to have an open conversation there and see where we can be of best use.","index":288,"end_time":777.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":774.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sure.","index":289,"end_time":780.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":780.2,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I''ll be quick on these.","index":290,"end_time":781.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":780.4,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I owe you all a brief, which I''m going to do this afternoon.","index":291,"end_time":786.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.2,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I owe that for you for Monday.","index":292,"end_time":787.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":786.08,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But each one of these bullets have a million things under it.","index":293,"end_time":790.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":787.96,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I just wanted to stick to the priorities.","index":294,"end_time":792,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":790.44,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So we have three months to test and validate the workflows.","index":295,"end_time":794.919,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":792,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Every month we will have multiple campaigns.","index":296,"end_time":799.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":795.48,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So every event is a campaign, every campaign is a campaign.","index":297,"end_time":803.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":799.84,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Every webinar, whether it''s nurture, webinar, et cetera.","index":298,"end_time":807.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":804.2,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I see those all populating now, Vivian, I meet with Claudia again this afternoon to make sure we''re capturing everything in eventbrite, which will go to the data box, finalizing the form implementations.","index":299,"end_time":818.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.67,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"For example, there''s a few more that are in the plan.","index":300,"end_time":823.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":818.59,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So the ROI calculators, the health assessments, just making sure that all of those are implemented.","index":301,"end_time":829.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":823.47,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"The modular newsletter we talked about, and then ABM architecture.","index":302,"end_time":833.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":830.27,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So, just so you''re aware, I was about to call you.","index":303,"end_time":837.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":833.67,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Duncan Flash from the past.","index":304,"end_time":840.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":837.61,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":305,"end_time":841.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":840.61,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Holy moly.","index":306,"end_time":841.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":841.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I did share an older Avanti.","index":307,"end_time":846.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":843.25,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That''s probably why.","index":308,"end_time":846.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":846.29,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Avanti.","index":309,"end_time":847.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":846.89,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Rico ABM document with Vivian so that she could see, you know, as we''re going into mining and food and Bev, what was required from us.","index":310,"end_time":858.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":847.41,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But I know that''s on the schedule for today as well, so I''ll start and Vivian can.","index":311,"end_time":863.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":858.85,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Can jump in.","index":312,"end_time":864.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":863.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":313,"end_time":866.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":865.81,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"This.","index":314,"end_time":866.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":866.17,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"These look.","index":315,"end_time":866.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":866.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"These look perfect.","index":316,"end_time":867.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":866.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Actually, the only thing I would say from a change management standpoint, the form that is the biggest impact item that we need to communicate a change to is The Hawk.","index":317,"end_time":879.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.81,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"The Hawk.","index":318,"end_time":880.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.13,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"The Hawk.","index":319,"end_time":881.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.89,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And the ought.","index":320,"end_time":882.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":881.53,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Registration forms, the referral forms.","index":321,"end_time":884.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.37,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"We need to make sure that we send Barb, that you send an email out when there''s a cutover from the old form to the new form.","index":322,"end_time":894.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":886.21,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Because that referral Mechanism, particularly the hawk one, feeds about 20% of our opportunities to our sales team.","index":323,"end_time":904.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":894.93,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"On the odd side, it''s like in the handfuls, but nevertheless, we need to.","index":324,"end_time":909.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.53,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Because it impacts another partner and it impacts our sales team.","index":325,"end_time":913.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.41,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And it''s not really a marketing forum, to be honest.","index":326,"end_time":916.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.97,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s a marketing service that we provide.","index":327,"end_time":918.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":916.41,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"We just need to make sure that those.","index":328,"end_time":921.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":919.65,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"That is like, there''s an email notification that''s done.","index":329,"end_time":924.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.17,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":330,"end_time":926.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":925.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":331,"end_time":927.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":926.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":332,"end_time":931.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":930.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Looks great.","index":333,"end_time":932.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":931.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":334,"end_time":934.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":933.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":335,"end_time":934.529,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":934.05,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And then so for abm, so Barb, with you sharing documentation, and I''m excited also because we''ve updated our ABM process pretty aggressively, so we''re able to use a bunch of new channels and everything.","index":336,"end_time":946.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":934.529,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll walk through that.","index":337,"end_time":947.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":946.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we do write a very comprehensive document that outlines who we''re talking to, where we''re talking to them, how we''re talking to them, and even goes down to details as like, this is the URL for the web hook, sending information from one system to another.","index":338,"end_time":961.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":948.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, as you guys have seen, hopefully in all of our documentation, we''re very transparent about everything.","index":339,"end_time":966.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":961.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that will give.","index":340,"end_time":967.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":966.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If anyone ever has a question, it could be, you know, the first day you look at the document or nine months later.","index":341,"end_time":973.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":968.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That is going to be our updated source of truth for everything that we''re running for sure.","index":342,"end_time":978.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":973.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this brings up a perfect point.","index":343,"end_time":980.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":978.45,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I think what I did, Colin, when I sent this over, I didn''t.","index":344,"end_time":984.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":981.01,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And this is great.","index":345,"end_time":985.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":984.69,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"What I didn''t do is split the current contact criteria versus ABM criteria.","index":346,"end_time":994.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":986.05,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I jammed it all into one email.","index":347,"end_time":995.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":994.13,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And so what you''re looking at is both.","index":348,"end_time":998.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":996.45,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So it''s when we''re looking at contacts to pull over and we''ll do the same with Aquarius.","index":349,"end_time":1004.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":999.81,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"When we spoke with Jason, anyone with an opportunity, we had 29,000.","index":350,"end_time":1008.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1004.05,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Well, whims being Wims, Rio and Classic, it should only go back two years.","index":351,"end_time":1014.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1008.78,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Zero to 90% prospect and customers waste and drinking water.","index":352,"end_time":1018.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1014.06,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"If.","index":353,"end_time":1018.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1018.62,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"If we have pulp and paper and food and.","index":354,"end_time":1020.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1018.98,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Great.","index":355,"end_time":1021.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1020.86,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"The second half of that is the abm, which has its own criteria.","index":356,"end_time":1025.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1021.34,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I just wanted to.","index":357,"end_time":1026.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.42,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, sorry about that.","index":358,"end_time":1027.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1026.3,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I.","index":359,"end_time":1027.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1027.3,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"No, no worries.","index":360,"end_time":1028.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1027.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"A light bulb went on this side.","index":361,"end_time":1029.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.18,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, I did.","index":362,"end_time":1030.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1029.9,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I didn''t split it up for you.","index":363,"end_time":1032.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.94,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"No, no worries.","index":364,"end_time":1033.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1032.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s why we have these conversations right to make sure all aligned.","index":365,"end_time":1035.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1033.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, that makes total sense.","index":366,"end_time":1037.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1035.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s great.","index":367,"end_time":1038.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1037.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we could definitely, you know, again, once we have those contact numbers finalized and everything and import them and tag them for the various campaigns and then set up ABM with that separate architecture as well.","index":368,"end_time":1048.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1038.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":369,"end_time":1049.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1049.3,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":370,"end_time":1050.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1049.74,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Of course all.","index":371,"end_time":1051.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And because I''m new to how new north or marketers in demand do abm, I''m working right now with two different groups on getting some of the foundational stuff for abm, like the Personas, the messaging and some initial content.","index":372,"end_time":1071.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.98,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"What else do you guys need from.","index":373,"end_time":1075.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1072.52,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"From us?","index":374,"end_time":1076.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1076.12,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like what are some of the foundational things that you need from us in order to set up abm?","index":375,"end_time":1081.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1076.72,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''d be great to get those now so that we''re building to spec versus just building what we think is needed.","index":376,"end_time":1088,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1081.2,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So any information there would be super helpful.","index":377,"end_time":1090.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1088.08,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, so a few foundational pieces.","index":378,"end_time":1092.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1090.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We need to know who we want communication coming from.","index":379,"end_time":1095.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1092.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''ll be a big piece.","index":380,"end_time":1096.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1095.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you know, Barb, you''ll remember we would choose Duncan for some because having like the head of the company for some large accounts is a good one, but also head of sales can, can have their own list.","index":381,"end_time":1106.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1096.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can, we can really put anyone into that and warm up emails and then we''ll also Tag into their LinkedIn profiles and send messages from them.","index":382,"end_time":1113.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1106.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other very vital piece is what is the offer?","index":383,"end_time":1117.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1114.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what is going to entice this person, you know, in the millions of emails and messages and ads that they see, what is going to make them click?","index":384,"end_time":1124.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1117.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And this is something that we often have a workshop around.","index":385,"end_time":1128.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1125.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So having to meet with the team and go through this, the way that we frame offers is.","index":386,"end_time":1133.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1128.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s that irresistible something tangible, something that shows them or kind of the metric that we operate on is people make almost 80% of their decision before they actually even talk to anyone.","index":387,"end_time":1145.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1133.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we need to give them a lot of information.","index":388,"end_time":1147.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1145.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They need to understand who Aquatic informatics is, what service they need and how they''re able to get it and what maybe is detrimental in their internal system right now.","index":389,"end_time":1157.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1147.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So maybe we can use the ROI calculator as part of that.","index":390,"end_time":1160.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1157.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Maybe it''s a whole new offer that''s a deep dive analysis on their current systems.","index":391,"end_time":1166.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1160.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If they''re able to provide some data, you know, there''s a few different ways that we can go down, but we often build custom solutions.","index":392,"end_time":1171.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1166.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One that''s been working very well for another client, for example, is a competitor benchmark analysis.","index":393,"end_time":1178.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1172.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They go in, they plug in some numbers from their HR team And it delivers a customized PDF download with where they''re sitting at, you know, below average or above average, and their exact numbers, and then points them to talking to the sales team.","index":394,"end_time":1193.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1178.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":395,"end_time":1195.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1194.74,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Those are really the two, like, mission critical things that we need as the foundation.","index":396,"end_time":1199.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1195.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":397,"end_time":1200.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1199.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s helpful.","index":398,"end_time":1201.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1201.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":399,"end_time":1203.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1203.34,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All right, any other questions around splitting ABM and Nurture.","index":400,"end_time":1209.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1206.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Enough for me.","index":401,"end_time":1212.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1211.42,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All right.","index":402,"end_time":1213.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1213.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":403,"end_time":1214.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1213.98,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And the only other thing I would say is that there''s two different ABM programs.","index":404,"end_time":1218.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1214.34,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"One is for Aquarius and one is for hawkwims.","index":405,"end_time":1221.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.26,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So they''re.","index":406,"end_time":1221.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1221.3,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"They''re separate.","index":407,"end_time":1222.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1221.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":408,"end_time":1223.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1222.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll document that in our infrastructure.","index":409,"end_time":1225.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1223.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":410,"end_time":1226.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1225.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":411,"end_time":1228.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1228.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so, and then going through the webinar workflows, Barb, so I know that you are sending over some additional content, I believe, for us to send out from an email update perspective.","index":412,"end_time":1239.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1229.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And the flow that we have in just making sure that we''re all aligned here is that you''re creating the zoom event and the landing page.","index":413,"end_time":1245.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1240.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we will create the form embedded and the thank you message as well as the workflow so that obviously all of them are connected and showing in HubSpot and sending automated emails.","index":414,"end_time":1258.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1246.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then on the day of, you know, thank you for attending or sorry you missed this event.","index":415,"end_time":1261.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1258.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, Barb, you would let us know when the on demand video is ready and we can just update that.","index":416,"end_time":1267.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1263.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":417,"end_time":1269.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''re all scheduled.","index":418,"end_time":1270.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1269.34,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So for you, Viv, there''s three this month and Terry''s and Dave Rutowskis are brand new, so they are scheduled a week prior for upload and testing.","index":419,"end_time":1281.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1270.34,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So we''re all good.","index":420,"end_time":1282.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1281.1,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":421,"end_time":1283.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1282.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":422,"end_time":1284.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1283.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so we do have a performance reporting plan.","index":423,"end_time":1288.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1285.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll send that over.","index":424,"end_time":1289.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1288.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t like to go through like a massive document on the call, but if you have any questions, please let us know.","index":425,"end_time":1294.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1289.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It just basically shows like a lot of it is based in data box, but what metrics are we tracking?","index":426,"end_time":1298.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1294.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Why are we tracking them and why are they important?","index":427,"end_time":1299.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1298.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''ll just do a quick preview here and there''s a table of contents breakdown as well of just really how we approach reporting.","index":428,"end_time":1307.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1300.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How are we breaking out different customer journeys?","index":429,"end_time":1310.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1308.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The lifecycle stages every bit of truth around HubSpot Databox, how we''re reporting.","index":430,"end_time":1315.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1310.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it is a lengthy document.","index":431,"end_time":1323.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1322.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":432,"end_time":1323.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1323.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''ll send this over for review.","index":433,"end_time":1325.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1323.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that also.","index":434,"end_time":1328.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1327.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Does it, does it include lead scoring in that?","index":435,"end_time":1331.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1328.69,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Is there like a section on lead scoring for this one?","index":436,"end_time":1334.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1331.81,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"We do have.","index":437,"end_time":1335.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1334.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Head boilerplate.","index":438,"end_time":1340.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1339.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And the only reason I''m asking that, Barb, I just got A message from Masara, and it was a really good question from her.","index":439,"end_time":1349.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1342.91,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"She wanted to get some education on lead scoring, and so I''ve directed her to you.","index":440,"end_time":1355.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1349.67,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"But the question I have is, have we changed our lead scoring a little bit in.","index":441,"end_time":1361.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1356.83,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"In this HubSpot move?","index":442,"end_time":1362.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1361.7,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I suspect we have, but you''re gonna have to refresh my memory because I''m.","index":443,"end_time":1366.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.78,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":444,"end_time":1368.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1368.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So in our initial conversations, we talked about updating the lead scoring framework, which I think would be a good idea.","index":445,"end_time":1374.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1368.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we just need like the exact.","index":446,"end_time":1376.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1375.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like this would be plus 10, or this would be plus 5 breakdown, and we can update the document to reflect that.","index":447,"end_time":1382.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1376.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that is essentially where we''re at.","index":448,"end_time":1385.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1383.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then once we have like, okay, if they, you know, engage with this page +5, we can build that into the workflow.","index":449,"end_time":1391.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1385.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, I have that.","index":450,"end_time":1394.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1392.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we didn''t change the.","index":451,"end_time":1396.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1394.69,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"The score from 100.","index":452,"end_time":1398.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1396.85,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"We just have to add some touch points, which I have.","index":453,"end_time":1402.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1398.69,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So now that we''ve.","index":454,"end_time":1403.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1402.37,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"We''re there, I''ll just resend it today, which is great.","index":455,"end_time":1406.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1403.81,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":456,"end_time":1406.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1406.13,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":457,"end_time":1407.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.69,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":458,"end_time":1408.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1407.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":459,"end_time":1411.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Great.","index":460,"end_time":1413.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1412.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":461,"end_time":1416.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1415.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And yeah, I love that doc.","index":462,"end_time":1417.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.1,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, if that can be our master, that.","index":463,"end_time":1419.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1417.74,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"That''s perfect.","index":464,"end_time":1420.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1419.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":465,"end_time":1420.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1420.26,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And we.","index":466,"end_time":1421.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1420.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anytime that anything changes, we update the document.","index":467,"end_time":1424.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1421.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just like all of our campaign plans and everything.","index":468,"end_time":1426.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1424.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s.","index":469,"end_time":1427.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.06,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s really great.","index":470,"end_time":1428.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.42,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Of course.","index":471,"end_time":1429.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1428.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":472,"end_time":1430.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1429.7,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And then, yeah, just will.","index":473,"end_time":1431.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1430.1,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Just will love that document.","index":474,"end_time":1433.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.78,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So that may.","index":475,"end_time":1435.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.22,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"That may be a document that you share with the, like the.","index":476,"end_time":1437.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1435.18,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Just the whole marketing team.","index":477,"end_time":1438.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1437.54,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":478,"end_time":1439.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1439.31,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":479,"end_time":1441.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1441.07,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":480,"end_time":1442.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1441.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I was going through requests for data box.","index":481,"end_time":1446.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1442.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So for GA4, there are certain filters that you can activate.","index":482,"end_time":1451.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1446.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So for example, total users we can break down by country.","index":483,"end_time":1454.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1451.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We cannot do that for all metrics just because of Google Analytics and cookies and tracking.","index":484,"end_time":1462.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1455.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so all of the available breakdowns that we''re able to Tag into from GA4 are already built into here.","index":485,"end_time":1470.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1463.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Unfortunately, just due to privacy laws, we can''t really tap into like this is the exact state that they''re in.","index":486,"end_time":1476.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1471.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then Barbado on this slide, also, you asked for a breakdown of companies that is not available in Google Analytics 4.","index":487,"end_time":1482.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1476.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think what you''re referring to is when we have the integration with factors.","index":488,"end_time":1486.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1483.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That was it.","index":489,"end_time":1487.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1487.37,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":490,"end_time":1488.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1487.97,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yes.","index":491,"end_time":1488.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1488.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that is something that we can do and we can do it through your points as well.","index":492,"end_time":1491.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1488.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That is six points a month, $600 for that platform per month.","index":493,"end_time":1495.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1491.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it is company level de anonymization.","index":494,"end_time":1498.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1495.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it is totally GDPR compliant.","index":495,"end_time":1501.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1498.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Doesn''t tell us individually who''s visiting the website, but it''ll track based on their company it does a whole bunch of IP matching to understand their personal profiles and their company profiles.","index":496,"end_time":1510.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1501.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can have a list of.","index":497,"end_time":1512.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1510.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is the.","index":498,"end_time":1512.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1512.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"These are the companies that have visited the website.","index":499,"end_time":1514.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1513.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"These are the amount of times and.","index":500,"end_time":1516.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1514.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The pages that they visited.","index":501,"end_time":1518.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1516.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll add that to our call today, Viv, so I can explain it further whether or not we want to go ahead with that.","index":502,"end_time":1524.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1519.27,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":503,"end_time":1525.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1524.7,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And then another question, like it says like versus previous period.","index":504,"end_time":1530.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1525.66,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Are we looking month to month, Are we looking over year over year?","index":505,"end_time":1534.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1530.54,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":506,"end_time":1534.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1534.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the cool thing about Kirin, Maine.","index":507,"end_time":1536.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1534.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, the cool thing about data box is you can actually change what, what dates you''re looking at down here.","index":508,"end_time":1541.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1536.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":509,"end_time":1541.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1541.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can say I want to look at the last.","index":510,"end_time":1543.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1541.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I want to look at.","index":511,"end_time":1546.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1545.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, it''s not going to be much for this year.","index":512,"end_time":1547.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1546.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":513,"end_time":1548.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1547.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I want to look at last year and then you can choose also a compare with.","index":514,"end_time":1555.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1548.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I want to compare with the previous period and then I hit apply.","index":515,"end_time":1559.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1555.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All of these will update and once they load then it''ll show the comparison metrics between those as long as they''re.","index":516,"end_time":1566.299,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1559.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Available in the systems.","index":517,"end_time":1567.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1566.299,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there we go.","index":518,"end_time":1571.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1570.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So now they''re showing the changes year over year.","index":519,"end_time":1573.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1571.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The LinkedIn company page, I was.","index":520,"end_time":1581.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1578.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, Barb.","index":521,"end_time":1582.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1581.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The one thing we need here, you would ask for a legion form completion rate.","index":522,"end_time":1586.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1582.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We do not have access currently to a AQI LinkedIn ads account and that''s what we would need that up.","index":523,"end_time":1592.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1586.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have the company page.","index":524,"end_time":1595.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1594.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t have the ads.","index":525,"end_time":1596.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1595.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Poor on my part.","index":526,"end_time":1598.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1597.23,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":527,"end_time":1598.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1598.27,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Sorry about that.","index":528,"end_time":1599.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1598.91,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"No, no worries.","index":529,"end_time":1600.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1599.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As soon as you invite us and I can, if you need me to send over the instructions for that again, I can.","index":530,"end_time":1604.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1600.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You would just add us as a partner on your account if you have a business manager.","index":531,"end_time":1609.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1606.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll.","index":532,"end_time":1611.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1610.28,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''ll get that to you today.","index":533,"end_time":1612.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1611.04,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":534,"end_time":1612.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1612.12,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":535,"end_time":1612.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1612.52,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Google search console.","index":536,"end_time":1617,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1616.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There was no feedback HubSpot so working on a breakdown of getting country into these so that we can break those down.","index":537,"end_time":1625.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1617,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It just requires us to build a custom metric instead of the out of the box ones.","index":538,"end_time":1629,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1625.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then also we''re working on.","index":539,"end_time":1633.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1632.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this is Salesforce, we were working on the events portion of it and so I''m building out list in HubSpot just to dynamically update based on anyone who''s registered so that we can see holistically how many webinar registrations we have.","index":540,"end_time":1647.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1634.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then if we want to break down by which webinar they did register.","index":541,"end_time":1651.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1647.569,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For, we can do so.","index":542,"end_time":1652.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1651.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":543,"end_time":1653.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1652.93,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So you can see me working on it here.","index":544,"end_time":1657.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is very tactical, but could you go back one step to show HubSpot for a second.","index":545,"end_time":1662.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1657.99,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":546,"end_time":1662.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1662.47,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And I know we barely have any contacts at all.","index":547,"end_time":1665.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1663.51,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Right.","index":548,"end_time":1665.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.59,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"In HubSpot.","index":549,"end_time":1666.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.83,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So when you show the event page and a registration, it has no owner.","index":550,"end_time":1670.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1666.63,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"You know, by default that owner is going to be me, which is marketing at.","index":551,"end_time":1675.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1670.87,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"If it''s events, it''s Claudia.","index":552,"end_time":1678.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.71,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''ve been going in and just kind of manually doing it.","index":553,"end_time":1681.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1678.39,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Is there a way to automate that?","index":554,"end_time":1682.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1681.15,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, we can update that in the workflow.","index":555,"end_time":1684.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1682.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if you all webinar registrations go to marketing or to Claudia.","index":556,"end_time":1687.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1684.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can just set that in the workflow.","index":557,"end_time":1689.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1687.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":558,"end_time":1690.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1690,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, thanks.","index":559,"end_time":1691.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1690.64,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Because once it gets in the hundreds and thousands, it''s going to be a lot.","index":560,"end_time":1694.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1691.4,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So let''s automate it.","index":561,"end_time":1697.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1694.28,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":562,"end_time":1698.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1697.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":563,"end_time":1700,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1699.44,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":564,"end_time":1700.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1700,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But yeah, we are working through the list here.","index":565,"end_time":1703.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1700.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is the biggest one to attack.","index":566,"end_time":1706.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1705.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that, that is going to take the most time of just making sure that we''re reporting on everything that Kyle wants to see.","index":567,"end_time":1711.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1706.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, yeah, once we get paid ads access, we can add all of these.","index":568,"end_time":1715.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1712.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then once we''ve set up the ABM infrastructure, we can add all of these.","index":569,"end_time":1718.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1715.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":570,"end_time":1719.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1719.03,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s great.","index":571,"end_time":1720.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1720.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":572,"end_time":1722.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1721.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I did see some questions down here of just tracking nurture.","index":573,"end_time":1725.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1722.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is this up?","index":574,"end_time":1727.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1725.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is this kind of up for discussion or where are we sitting with this currently?","index":575,"end_time":1731.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1727.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that''s the last question that I had.","index":576,"end_time":1734.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1732.47,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"If you guys have another minute or two.","index":577,"end_time":1736.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1734.67,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So Vivian, you''d ask like, how are we tracking nurture?","index":578,"end_time":1740.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1736.71,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And I think Jess asked me the same thing.","index":579,"end_time":1741.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1740.26,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So all the nurture Campaigns are in HubSpot, which I showed you just very briefly.","index":580,"end_time":1746.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1741.82,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"We capture everything in there.","index":581,"end_time":1748.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1746.46,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"The net Result is an MQL and SQL.","index":582,"end_time":1752.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1748.54,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"We can see how it''s performing in HubSpot.","index":583,"end_time":1754.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1752.06,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''m not sure how much we need to show in the data box because when you nurture something, there''s a result which then is captured.","index":584,"end_time":1763.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1754.86,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"MQL SQL.","index":585,"end_time":1765.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1764.12,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But like, are you managing the MAL pipeline?","index":586,"end_time":1769.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1765.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like is it, is it, is it an mal report?","index":587,"end_time":1772.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1769.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I think that''s what I was envisioning.","index":588,"end_time":1773.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1772.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like, are we like, like looking at where the mals are tracking?","index":589,"end_time":1778.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1773.88,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Oh yeah.","index":590,"end_time":1779.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.08,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So we, we check mals in the data box.","index":591,"end_time":1782.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.84,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":592,"end_time":1782.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1782.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"SQLs, etc, there are layers within those.","index":593,"end_time":1786.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.48,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":594,"end_time":1787.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1786.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":595,"end_time":1788.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.04,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I just, you know, let''s say I do five nurture campaigns a month and all of these people are within one, two to five campaigns.","index":596,"end_time":1797.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1788.44,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All of that is captured within the event in HubSpot.","index":597,"end_time":1801.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1798,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I''m not sure.","index":598,"end_time":1802.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1801.76,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I don''t know that I know the answer to that quickly until we start to track it.","index":599,"end_time":1806.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1802.72,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":600,"end_time":1807.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1807.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But, yeah, that''s all I. Yeah.","index":601,"end_time":1810.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.76,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"What''s possible.","index":602,"end_time":1812.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1811.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":603,"end_time":1813.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1812.72,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And the reason why I''m asking is, like, you know, it''d be interesting to know if the nurture campaigns are playing a bigger role than, like, the web.","index":604,"end_time":1822.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1813.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":605,"end_time":1823.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1822.9,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like, than the paid webinars.","index":606,"end_time":1824.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1823.58,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Because I think my hypothesis is that a lot of the nurture work that you do is going to be, like, very impactful into converting things into MQLs.","index":607,"end_time":1834.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1824.86,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And so having some kind of a metric to say, hey, these nurture programs moved 20% of our final MQL results versus other sources.","index":608,"end_time":1846.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1834.7,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Like, I see nurture as a source, I guess.","index":609,"end_time":1847.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1846.02,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, let''s work on that.","index":610,"end_time":1851.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1848.75,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":611,"end_time":1852.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1851.87,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"For instance, you know, we''ll have a, you know, water world in November.","index":612,"end_time":1855.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1852.39,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Pulled everything out, drop them into the most simplistic, constant contact ever.","index":613,"end_time":1861.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1856.11,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"But, yeah, that''s also a nurture plus paid, plus social, so.","index":614,"end_time":1865.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1861.79,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Right, that''s.","index":615,"end_time":1866.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1865.47,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"That''s true.","index":616,"end_time":1866.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1866.31,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So, yeah, yeah, that''s.","index":617,"end_time":1868.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s definitely a thing to keep in mind, you know, especially when we''re working with a scrappy set of tools for data capture.","index":618,"end_time":1874.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1868.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, if you guys.","index":619,"end_time":1875.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1874.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you had the budget for, like, a dream data, which is like between 100 and 250,000 a year to track everything that someone did.","index":620,"end_time":1882.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1876.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what I would say is we could have like, a first attribution.","index":621,"end_time":1885.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1883.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, how did they land in the CRM?","index":622,"end_time":1887.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1885.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then a last attribution, what did convert them to customer.","index":623,"end_time":1890.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1887.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But oftentimes you''ll see, like, they engage with several nurture emails, they engage with a few paid ads.","index":624,"end_time":1896.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1891.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s.","index":625,"end_time":1897.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1896.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s often more than one channel in their journey.","index":626,"end_time":1899.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1897.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":627,"end_time":1900.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1899.6,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And you know what?","index":628,"end_time":1900.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1900.08,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s a nice to have, like, you know, it just.","index":629,"end_time":1902.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1900.76,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"It''s a nice data point to have.","index":630,"end_time":1904.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1902.8,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":631,"end_time":1904.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1904.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And all of it will be tracked in there, but not a contact record as well.","index":632,"end_time":1907.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1904.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not a.","index":633,"end_time":1908.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1907.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not a.","index":634,"end_time":1908.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1908.39,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Not a must.","index":635,"end_time":1909.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1908.95,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"We''ll figure it out.","index":636,"end_time":1910.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1909.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":637,"end_time":1910.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1910.55,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":638,"end_time":1911.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1910.83,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Apologies, I have to run.","index":639,"end_time":1912.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1911.51,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"I''ve got another meeting.","index":640,"end_time":1913.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1912.67,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"But thank you so much, team.","index":641,"end_time":1915.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1913.99,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"What a great start to the year.","index":642,"end_time":1917.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1915.99,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"And again, thank you so much for.","index":643,"end_time":1919.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1917.55,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Is it only been two and a half months.","index":644,"end_time":1921.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1919.59,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"You guys have done a tremendous amount of work.","index":645,"end_time":1923.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1921.23,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"So much.","index":646,"end_time":1924.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1923.11,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Much thanks to that.","index":647,"end_time":1925.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1924.39,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Yeah, of course, we''re happy to help.","index":648,"end_time":1926.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1925.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Happy to be a partner.","index":649,"end_time":1927.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1926.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, bye.","index":650,"end_time":1929.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1928.71,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"Bye.","index":651,"end_time":1930.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1929.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Feel better, Vivian.","index":652,"end_time":1930.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1930.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":653,"end_time":1931.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1931.28,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"You too.","index":654,"end_time":1932.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1931.8,"speaker_name":"Vivian Chan"},{"text":"You too.","index":655,"end_time":1932.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1932.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks, everybody.","index":656,"end_time":1934.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1933.2,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah, Barb, the only other.","index":657,"end_time":1936.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1934.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We already went through the newsletter, and.","index":658,"end_time":1939.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1936.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then you have access to Pulse, so.","index":659,"end_time":1941.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1939.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is there anything that we missed that you wanted to go through.","index":660,"end_time":1943.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1941.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that was it.","index":661,"end_time":1944.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1943.68,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That was.","index":662,"end_time":1944.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1944.6,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That was lightning Round.","index":663,"end_time":1945.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1944.96,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So I appreciate it.","index":664,"end_time":1947.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1946.4,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And, yeah, try to keep it in.","index":665,"end_time":1948.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1947.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re only three minutes.","index":666,"end_time":1949.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1948.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Keep it moving.","index":667,"end_time":1950.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1950.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But, yeah, thank you so much, you guys.","index":668,"end_time":1952.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1950.84,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":669,"end_time":1954.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1954.24,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"As I''ve said before, that just.","index":670,"end_time":1957.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1954.64,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"My closing is that, first of all, thank you.","index":671,"end_time":1960.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1957.16,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Vivian is putting forth today a recommendation to Hawk, which is a lot bigger than us, to move to HubSpot with you guys this year.","index":672,"end_time":1973.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1960.24,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"And she asked me for Tristan''s information today to give to the IT guys.","index":673,"end_time":1979.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1973.44,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"So hopefully that''s.","index":674,"end_time":1981.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1979.08,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That''s a really good lead to start the year off.","index":675,"end_time":1982.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1981.04,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"That''s amazing.","index":676,"end_time":1983.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1983.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":677,"end_time":1984.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1984.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, you deserve a few more hats, for sure.","index":678,"end_time":1987.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1984.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m gonna put this one on.","index":679,"end_time":1989.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1988.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m doing it.","index":680,"end_time":1990.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1989.82,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"There we go.","index":681,"end_time":1991.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1990.58,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"There you go.","index":682,"end_time":1991.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1991.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There we go.","index":683,"end_time":1992.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1991.78,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"I love it.","index":684,"end_time":1992.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1992.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That looks great.","index":685,"end_time":1993.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1992.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me get a picture real quick.","index":686,"end_time":1996.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1994.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I gotta show this to the team.","index":687,"end_time":1997.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1996.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, it''s not.","index":688,"end_time":2000.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2000.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me screenshot.","index":689,"end_time":2001.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2000.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We got our recorder in here.","index":690,"end_time":2002.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2001.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll be good.","index":691,"end_time":2002.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2002.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":692,"end_time":2004.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2003.38,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"All right.","index":693,"end_time":2004.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2004.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Bye, guys.","index":694,"end_time":2005.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2004.98,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"},{"text":"Bye.","index":695,"end_time":2005.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2005.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you, Barb.","index":696,"end_time":2006.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2005.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Take care.","index":697,"end_time":2007.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2007.06,"speaker_name":"Barb Willans"}],"dateString":"2026-01-02T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/89786281993?pwd=li2lwrSFpmITXPKEdOBBgaXPwh8ONO.1","participants":["guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,barb.willans@aquaticinformatics.com","guille.santana@marketersind