s dialo but now they''re doing.","index":157,"end_time":701.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":693.99,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"They''re actually doing data center operations or something like that.","index":158,"end_time":706.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":701.61,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, so we should remove them it seems.","index":159,"end_time":708.89,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":706.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, you can definitely remove Media Klan because he''s very familiar with this at all.","index":160,"end_time":714.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":709.85,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"He used to be one of the primary.","index":161,"end_time":716.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":714.25,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s how easy to find him.","index":162,"end_time":718.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":716.97,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That''s kind of a funny coincidence that you found him because he''s the main guy that we kind of initially sold digital to at Fujitsu but then he.","index":163,"end_time":729.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":718.21,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So remove Michael but keep Manage now.","index":164,"end_time":732.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":729.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think Manage now you can also remove because they.","index":165,"end_time":736.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":733.27,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"They.","index":166,"end_time":737.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":736.87,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"They actually had digitalo and they.","index":167,"end_time":740.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":737.59,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"They''re not doing really IT consulting anymore.","index":168,"end_time":744.47,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":740.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":169,"end_time":745.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":744.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},